## 10. Accessibility - Mobile

### 10.1 Required Attributes

**Form Inputs:**
- `autocomplete` attributes (e.g., `autocomplete="given-name"`)
- `required` for mandatory fields
- `aria-label` for icon-only buttons

**Interactive Elements:**
- `aria-live="polite"` for dynamic content (form success/error)
- `aria-busy="true"` during form submission
- Focus states: `focus:outline-none focus:border-white`

**Semantic HTML:**
- Use `<form>` for forms
- Use `<button type="submit">` for submit buttons
- Use proper heading hierarchy (`<h1>`, `<h2>`, etc.)

### 10.2 Touch Targets

**Rule:** Minimum touch target size: `48px × 48px` (matches input height)

**Implementation:**
```astro
<!-- ✅ CORRECT: Adequate touch target -->
<button class="h-[48px] px-[24px]">Submit</button>

<!-- ❌ WRONG: Too small -->
<button class="h-[32px] px-[12px]">Submit</button>
```

